01:01:00,156 --> 01:01:01,907
Stop it, okay?

787
01:01:03,618 --> 01:01:06,995
You don't play dumb
with me and I won't play dumb with you.

788
01:01:07,247 --> 01:01:08,956
I miss him, too!

789
01:01:10,375 --> 01:01:11,834
I miss him, too.

790
01:01:12,168 --> 01:01:14,294
I miss him every day.

791
01:01:15,713 --> 01:01:19,508
I loved him like I
never loved a guy and I don't love guys.

792
01:01:19,759 --> 01:01:22,428
You don't have
an excuse. You quit!

793
01:01:22,929 --> 01:01:25,013
You quit. You gave up.

794
01:01:29,310 --> 01:01:31,562
He never quit anything
until it killed him.

795
01:01:31,729 --> 01:01:35,732
That was his way.
There are worse ways and you sure found one.

796
01:01:36,443 --> 01:01:40,154
(SOBBING) I can't
live without him.

797
01:01:40,822 --> 01:01:42,072
Bullshit!

798
01:01:45,702 --> 01:01:46,994
Bullshit.

799
01:01:53,543 --> 01:01:56,128
That's Al coming
in from San Diego.

800
01:01:56,880 --> 01:01:59,089
We'll talk to him.
He's a good guy.

801
01:02:00,216 --> 01:02:03,385
He always sees
the funny side. Want to cut your engine?

802
01:02:26,409 --> 01:02:28,327
Reminds me of
a girl I knew.

803
01:02:32,290 --> 01:02:33,916
How are you doing, Linda?

804
01:03:03,780 --> 01:03:05,531
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

805
01:03:07,450 --> 01:03:08,825
(LIGHTNING CRACKS)

806
01:03:13,414 --> 01:03:15,958
You'd better land
and sit this one out.

807
01:03:16,751 --> 01:03:18,335
And make it fast.

808
01:04:34,287 --> 01:04:37,664
MAN: (CHUCKLES)
Walk! Don't walk!

809
01:04:39,083 --> 01:04:41,710
No swimming! No entry!

810
01:04:42,045 --> 01:04:44,755
It's a fact.
I saw the signs. A-ha!

811
01:04:47,717 --> 01:04:49,968
I saw all the signs.

812
01:04:50,595 --> 01:04:52,012
Exit!

813
01:04:52,555 --> 01:04:57,225
Falling rocks!
Jesus saves! Save water! Turn off the lights! Click.

814
01:04:57,310 --> 01:04:58,352
Hi.

815
01:04:58,436 --> 01:04:59,978
Danger!
Keep off the grass!

816
01:05:00,063 --> 01:05:03,065
I saw the signs.
No shoes, no shirt, no service.

817
01:05:03,524 --> 01:05:06,234
Yield. Tow away.
Use other door.

818
01:05:06,361 --> 01:05:08,612
That's no way
to live. (SIGHS)

819
01:05:10,239 --> 01:05:12,324
No wonder I'm not
giving lessons in love.

820
01:05:12,408 --> 01:05:13,700
Lessons in love.

821
01:05:14,077 --> 01:05:16,328
I can turn a plane
on a wingtip.

822
01:05:16,412 --> 01:05:19,039
I can stall a plane
at 1,000 feet and come up smiling.

823
01:05:19,123 --> 01:05:20,540
Come up smiling.

824
01:05:24,587 --> 01:05:26,254
But that don't
matter a damn.

825
01:05:26,422 --> 01:05:27,756
Matter a damn.

826
01:05:32,929 --> 01:05:34,012
You can hear me.

827
01:05:34,222 --> 01:05:35,430
You can hear me.

828
01:05:35,556 --> 01:05:36,765
I can hear you fine.

829
01:05:38,142 --> 01:05:41,103
Hey, old-timer.
Just passing through?

830
01:05:41,604 --> 01:05:44,481
Ted, listen to me.
(REPEATS)

831
01:05:46,776 --> 01:05:48,360
How did you
know my name?

832
01:05:48,611 --> 01:05:52,531
Maybe crazy old hobos
are like radio stations,

833
01:05:52,907 --> 01:05:56,076
picking up voices
from people who've gone off the air.

834
01:05:56,786 --> 01:06:00,789
So tune in, kid.
I want to get this through to you.

835
01:06:01,124 --> 01:06:02,290
Get through to you.

836
01:06:02,375 --> 01:06:04,418
With me,
it was Dorinda.

837
01:06:04,752 --> 01:06:06,002
Dorinda.
(GASPS)

838
01:06:06,629 --> 01:06:08,046
When you meet
the woman you love...

839
01:06:08,131 --> 01:06:09,256
The woman you love.

840
01:06:09,340 --> 01:06:10,549
Not Dorinda,
the one he loves.

841
01:06:10,633 --> 01:06:11,800
Dorinda,
the one you love.

842
01:06:11,884 --> 01:06:14,219
After you're dead
you can never

843
01:06:14,303 --> 01:06:15,429
go back for her.

844
01:06:15,513 --> 01:06:16,596
Go back for her.

845
01:06:16,681 --> 01:06:18,849
You can't turn around
and do it right.

846
01:06:18,933 --> 01:06:20,559
Turn around.
Do it right!

847
01:06:21,644 --> 01:06:23,186
That's not what I mean.

848
01:06:23,312 --> 01:06:25,397
What I'm trying to say is,
I've seen the signs.

849
01:06:25,481 --> 01:06:27,023
No exit. No passing.
No parking.

850
01:06:27,525 --> 01:06:29,151
No U-turn.

851
01:06:31,320 --> 01:06:33,780
I'm going back to get
my Air Attack card.

852
01:06:36,242 --> 01:06:38,243
(MIMICKING AIRPLANE)

853
01:06:48,004 --> 01:06:52,340
Tower, find Al Yackey
and tell him Ted Baker wants to talk.

854
01:06:52,425 --> 01:06:57,763
I like you this way, Ted.
You're revved up and full of moxie.

855
01:07:17,033 --> 01:07:18,533
I hate you!

856
01:07:18,785 --> 01:07:21,369
Charlie! Somebody!

857
01:07:22,371 --> 01:07:24,456
In this world,
you have to go out

858
01:07:24,540 --> 01:07:26,541
and get what you want.
Follow me?

859
01:07:33,716 --> 01:07:35,467
Rachel, slow down.

860
01:07:36,260 --> 01:07:37,677
Where is she taking us?

861
01:07:42,058 --> 01:07:43,225
Ted!

862
01:07:44,393 --> 01:07:46,061
Don't "Follow Me"!

863
01:07:51,734 --> 01:07:52,943
Ted.

864
01:07:54,445 --> 01:07:56,363
