872
01:09:10,938 --> 01:09:11,980
You all right?

873
01:09:12,064 --> 01:09:13,148
I'm okay.

874
01:09:24,744 --> 01:09:26,411
(DORINDA DIALING)

875
01:09:32,084 --> 01:09:33,168
(GRUNTS)

876
01:09:33,502 --> 01:09:35,670
Al Yackey, please.
(SNIFFS)

877
01:09:39,300 --> 01:09:41,051
Yes, it's me.

878
01:09:41,385 --> 01:09:43,178
No, I'm fine.

879
01:09:43,763 --> 01:09:45,972
You should come
down here and see

880
01:09:46,057 --> 01:09:48,266
