I'm just renting.

882
01:09:56,317 --> 01:09:57,817
Okay, I'll see you.

883
01:09:59,487 --> 01:10:00,987
Hello, Dorinda.

884
01:10:04,533 --> 01:10:06,159
I'm right here.

885
01:10:07,828 --> 01:10:09,412
I'm sitting here...

886
01:10:10,373 --> 01:10:12,332
