887
01:10:17,213 --> 01:10:19,130
I know you can't see me,

888
01:10:21,425 --> 01:10:22,884
but

889
01:10:23,678 --> 01:10:25,261
I can see you.

890
01:10:27,473 --> 01:10:31,309
I can see your hair.
It's almost in your...

891
01:10:33,062 --> 01:10:34,688
That's my girl.

892
01:10:36,983 --> 01:10:39,401
You're still my girl,
