893
01:10:45,241 --> 01:10:46,741
I thought so.

894
01:10:51,622 --> 01:10:53,873
God, I wish
we'd met sooner.

895
01:10:56,794 --> 01:10:59,379
I wish we'd met
when we were five.

896
01:11:00,631 --> 01:11:03,383
I'd have swept
you right off your three-wheeler.

897
01:11:07,263 --> 01:11:09,681
You've still got
a funny face.

898
01:11:14,770 --> 01:11:17,230
I can't believe
how much I miss you.

899
01:11:20,401 --> 01:11:21,651
I miss you

