at you and I said, "That's her."

906
01:11:44,467 --> 01:11:46,092
"That's the one."

907
01:11:46,218 --> 01:11:47,635
Do you remember?

908
01:11:48,554 --> 01:11:50,847
I walked up
to you and I said...

909
